Deployment
This portfolio is deployed using GitHub Pages.
Local Development
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/solomon-onyiba/solomon-onyiba.github.io.git
# Navigate to directory
cd solomon-onyiba.github.io
# Open in browser (or use Live Server extension)
open index.html
Deployment Steps
1. Push changes to main branch
2. Go to Repository Settings → Pages
3. Source: Deploy from Branch → Select main
4. Site will be live at https://yourusername.github.io/
